{"tid":165904,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛上一個密封罩既你","createTime":"2017-03-21T16:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T18:10:30.000Z","uid":63272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edce9b25953964260d1c6cb0185da82eed95e572","tid":165904,"uid":63272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:54:57.000Z","msg":"唉煩惱緊 <br />\n鍾意左個個係自我保護得好好既人<br />\n一早就比晒signal話自己唔拍拖 再遇唔到一個最愛既人<br />\n已經用左段時間去了解同埋鼓勵接受新戀情<br />\n但而家連msg都唔理 ig又無睇過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好痛<br />\n用五十年融化你 成就金禧一吻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a730b4f9295e2e73c66019f6d6c7d85c9fda11a","tid":165904,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"應該有約過佢單獨出街瓜？"},{"pid":"3ffd2071be21cdf81d02308db8c0fe0133178ca8","tid":165904,"uid":63272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該有約過佢單獨出街瓜？</blockquote><br />\n約過好多次 都唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪無希望"},{"pid":"fcee60ab1b40731bcc616edf4597aea9320e78aa","tid":165904,"uid":72769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:05:00.000Z","msg":"咁樣窄啲喎<br />\n試下一大班人約出去<br />\n做住朋友先"},{"pid":"d9b35866a55bcac90e45b49da1dfda08f6e2e17e","tid":165904,"uid":63272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T17:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁樣窄啲喎<br />\n試下一大班人約出去<br />\n做住朋友先</blockquote><br />\n好小共同朋友架我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />